		<br>
		<b>Bill Trost:</b>  Right, the reason why its there is because if we did as elaborate a texture on the outdoor zones like some of the indoor zones, basically , we’d have much fewer NPCs because the CPU couldn’t handle it.  We’re basically maxing the CPU at where it is.  And we’d much rather use the CPU to have more monsters than having the monsters be incrementally smarter.&nbsp;<br>
